sequenceDiagram
  participant Volunteer
  participant UI
  participant API
  participant DB

  Volunteer->>UI: Open opportunities page
  UI->>API: GET /api/events
  API->>DB: Fetch published opportunities
  DB-->>API: Opportunities list
  API-->>UI: Opportunities JSON
  UI-->>Volunteer: Show opportunities

  Volunteer->>UI: Apply / Join opportunity
  UI->>API: POST /api/events/:id/join
  API->>DB: Add volunteer request
  DB-->>API: Updated event
  API-->>UI: Request sent
  UI-->>Volunteer: Status = Pending

  Organization->>UI: Review applicants
  UI->>API: PUT /api/events/:eventId/approve/:userId
  API->>DB: Approve volunteer
  DB-->>API: Updated event
  API-->>UI: Approved
  UI-->>Organization: Volunteer accepted

  Organization->>UI: Mark attendance
  UI->>API: POST /api/volunteer/log
  API->>DB: Save volunteer log
  DB-->>API: Log saved
  API-->>UI: Hours recorded
